INFORMACOES-ADICIONAIS.DESCRICAO-INFORMACOES-ADICIONAIS:
International academic agreement signed in order to strengthen the co-operation between the institutions that they represent and, thus, contribute toward giving a more international focus to the studies taught therein, and to promote activities and projects of mutual interest, particularly concerning:
-the organisation of seminars, courses, workshops, summer schools, internships/placements, and other similar initiatives;
-the development of studies and collaborative research projects;
-the organisation of meetings, congresses, lectures etc. to improve the exchange of knowledge and experience;
-the exchange of documentation: works, reviews, pedagogical documentation, exhibitions;
-the exchange of teachers, researchers, technicians and students.

